Alpha - Class in geoquant
The Alpha geoquant is defined on vertex and is used to modify the calculation of edge length as follows: l_ij = alpha_i * r_i^2 + alpha_j * r_j^2 + 2 * r_i * r_j * eta_ij An alpha geoquant does not depend on any other quantities.
